{
  "stem": "3360.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was the name of the school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called by the name of the street where it was located.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what I would like to bring out is the fact that we eventually had to move from there after four years, but we had some very wonderful neighbors, Gentile people-- the Paulsons and the Alrichs and I can't remember one other name in particular.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had, in that street, and the streets-- the other streets that ran parallel for it, to it-- excuse me-- were actually a-- almost a-- you could almost say a hot bed of early Nazis, which apparently my parents didn't know when we first moved there.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One picture I have in my mind that I'll never forget is the sea of swastika flags that were hung there for a certain occasion.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Election, Hitler's birthday, or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a sea of the red with the white and the black swastika inside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And while there were, of course, some people who did not fly that flag until they had to, it was an overwhelming picture.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You could walk down that street and if you saw that, it, it was a very scary thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- so anyway, while we lived there, I attended this, this school, as I mentioned, in the Kielort Allee, and-- [CLEARING THROAT] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It, it was a wonderful experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It-- I-- the four years there was very happy years in my life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had a lot of friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had a marvelous teacher, and we-- I loved to go to school.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
